-- NESTS: bracket forms with infix rune

=== simple infix | 80
(a + b)

=== three operands | 80
(a + b + c)

=== curly with comma | 80
{a , b , c}

=== bracket with bar | 80
[x | y | z]

=== nested infix | 80
(a + (b * c))

=== clear infix | 80
a + b

=== trailing comma | 80
(foo ,)

=== trailing plus | 80
(bar +)

